snippet.title: Astral Doorway
snippet.description:
The purpose of this channel is to spread awareness about the reality and practice of awakening consciousness through the Three Factors of Awakening Consciousness (Death, Birth & Sacrifice); ultimately pointing humanity to the Path of Internal Initiation into the Sacred Mysteries.

To do this, we learn practical wisdom to begin gaining our own "Gnosis" (knowledge from direct experience as opposed to mere beliefs). There are many videos that cover a range of topics, go to the 'Playlists' section and choose where you want to begin.

If you want to donate, you can join the Discord group for live lectures, Q&As, early-access episodes, forums & more. This also helps others by supporting the channel and our Gnostic mission in bringing this knowledge to the Philippines: https://www.patreon.com/astraldoorway üôè

You can also donate at: https://www.gnosiscebu.org/donate ü§ç
